OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man killed in
OL,4,Ctriple stabbing
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after a
OL,7,Ftriple stabbing have paid tribute to
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FWayne Broadhurst died after being
OL,11,Fstabbed in Midhurst Gardens in
OL,12,FUxbridge on Monday 27 October 2025.
OL,14,FIn a tribute to the 49-year-old, his
OL,15,Ffamily said: "Wayne Broadhurst was a
OL,16,Fdevoted and hardworking man who spent
OL,17,Fhis life serving his community as a
OL,18,Fwaste services worker.
