OL,6,F"He worked hard his whole life, never
OL,7,Fshying away from improving his
OL,8,Fcommunity.
OL,10,F"His love for animals showed the
OL,11,Fgentle heart behind his strong work
OL,12,Fethic, and his passion for Liverpool
OL,13,FFC was something he loved to share
OL,14,Fwith others.
OL,16,F"His loss has left a deep void, not
OL,17,Fonly in the hearts of his family and
OL,18,Ffriends, but across the community he
OL,19,Fquietly cared for.
