OL,6,F"Wayne will be remembered for his
OL,7,Fkindness, his loyalty, and his genuine
OL,8,Fwillingness to help others. His
OL,9,Fabsence is felt profoundly, and his
OL,10,Fmemory will continue to live on in our
OL,11,Fcommunity."
OL,13,FHis partner Ann Newman has also paid
OL,14,Ftribute to Mr Broadhurst as "a
OL,15,Fhardworking man who dedicated his life
OL,16,Fto serving his community".
