OL,6,FWriting on a GoFundMe page, Ms Newman
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are heartbroken to announce
OL,8,Fthe tragic loss of our beloved Wayne
OL,9,FBroadhurst, a hardworking man who
OL,10,Fdedicated his life to serving his
OL,11,Fcommunity through his work in waste
OL,12,Fcollection."
OL,14,FSince the fundraiser was launched on
OL,15,FWednesday, more than #35,000 has been
OL,16,Fraised, which Ms Newman said will go
OL,17,Ftowards funeral costs, support for his
OL,18,Frelatives and "helping to honour his
OL,19,Flife in the way he deserves".
