OL,6,FOn Thursday 30 October, an Afghan
OL,7,Fmigrant appeared in court charged with
OL,8,Fmurdering Mr Broadhurst.
OL,10,FSafi Dawood is also accused of
OL,11,Fattempting to murder his landlord
OL,12,FShahzad Farrukh, 45, and a 14-year-old
OL,13,Fboy.
OL,15,FThe 22-year-old, who lived with Mr
OL,16,FFarrukh as his lodger at an address in
OL,17,FMidhurst Gardens, has also been
OL,18,Fcharged with one count of possessing
OL,19,Fan offensive weapon, Westminster
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court heard.
